<title>SOUTH AFRICA: Lithosaver buys Self Adhering Products.</title>
<headline>Lithosaver buys Self Adhering Products.</headline>
<dateline>JOHANNESBURG 1996-08-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Lithosaver Systems Ltd said on Friday it had reached agreement to buy Self Adhering Products &amp; Associates (Pty) Ltd for 15.41 million rand in cash.</p>
<p>Assuming the acquisition had been effective in the year to end-February 1996, Lithsaver earnings per share would have increased by 2.7 cents to 20.0 cents, the company said.</p>
<p>Lithosaver first said it was negotiating to buy the adhesive label firm on July 31.</p>
<p>-- Johannesburg newsroom +27 11 482 1003</p>
</text>
